MLPLAY_CLASS_TOOLTIP:
The main block for playing the game.
The program in the "initialize" section will be executed once before the game starts.
The program in the "update" section will be executed once every frame in the game. You can get the current scene information in the game here, and return the next action.
After the game is over, the program in the "reset" will be executed once before the next game starts.
